{"title":"NetFlow Intro","type":"markdown","params":{"fontSize":10,"openLinksInNewTab":false,"markdown":"Use the [NetFlow Dashboard](#/dashboard/99d1b510-72b3-11e8-9159-894bd7d62352) to explore this data

NetFlow data is loaded via the following methods:
* Files in the `/logstash/nfarch/` directory.
  * NOTE: Files must be in the format from the supplied `nfdump2sof-elk.sh` script: `nfdump2sof-elk.sh [-e <exporter ip address>] -r <path to nfcapd-based netflow data>`
* Zeek `conn.log` files in the `/logstash/zeek/` directory.
* NetFlow v5 or v9 network messages sent to UDP port 9995"},"aggs":[]}
